snippet.description:
Inspiring Marilyn Monroe Quotes Definitely Inspire You #shorts

Marilyn Monroe was an American actress, model and singer. Famous for playing comedic "blonde bombshell" characters, she became one of the most popular sex symbols of the 1950s and early 1960s and was emblematic of the era's sexual revolution.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Marilyn Monroe. The best quotes and aphorisms of Marilyn Monroe that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Marilyn Monroe are definitely worth your time.

Thank you for watching!
